Dear Scan Translate Users. last week was very difficult for the project. a critical error occurred that led to the unavailability of the service worldwide. but we fixed it ! We thank everyone for your support and patience and we apologize for any inconvenience you ve experienced since the service was unavailable. Sincerely yours AISBERG Team

NEW ! iPhone X UI optimized iOS 12 support NEW ! Snap Mode get instant image translation New ! iCloud sync Now all your scans and Translations will sync automatically with your iCloud storage Minor bug fixes. We will keep updating Scan Translate for you !!!
File Manager bug fixes

Meet the NEW Scan Translate App! NICE and more intuitive UI GREAT NEW features: send PDF converted docs save all your scans within the App Scans Library combine text and images into multipage documents iCloud synchronization: you will never lose your data again iMessage support: make scans directly from iMessage and send extracted text and translations to your friends Danish UI localization! Special thanks to Mads Houpt for help! Many thanks to everyone for your feedbacks and support! WE ALWAYS ARE HAPPY TO HEAR FROM YOU TO MAKE THINGS BETTER!

iOS 9.0.2 updated. Improved camera algorithm. Korean localization is available! Now you may delete files from history by swipe Translation issues resolved. Thanks to ALL OUR USERS for your feedbacks and support!

We prepeared a fundamental Update for our Users! iPhone 6 and 6 support. Fix Camera and Gallery access on iOS 6. OCR algorythm improved. Some UI improvement. Fix App s crashes while you import photo from gallery. More daily turns for OCR. Multiple file selection in App s History . Users that have foreign language difficulties or dyslexia asked for Voice Speed. This is a new feature which is NOW AVAILABLE! Thank you for staying with us while we update our app to make it more user friendly.
Minor bug fixes. We are fixed a bug with blurred images. More Target languages : Kazakh Malagasy Malayalam Myanmar Burmese Sesotho Sinhala Sundanese Tajic Uzbek
